title: Gunman kills three in Belgium's Liege
text:
Gunman kills three in Belgium's Liege Tuesday, May 29, 2018 - 01:00
A gunman killed two police officers and a passer-by on Tuesday before being shot dead in the center of the Belgian city of Liege. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
